_:N37d969a3392043b99de5f71784ef38cb <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Hamish Falconer was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office on 18 July 2024. He was elected as the MP for Lincoln in July 2024.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n  <p>Follow Hamish on X: <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://twitter.com/HFalconerMP\">@HFalconerMP</a>.</p>\n</div>\n" .
